Actors do a fine job but they're just tools to progress the story and there is nothing interesting about them and at a point you just want to scream at them for being so dumb and making stupid decisions. Girl who plays Morgan did fine but nohing memorable. Movie is choppy and uneventful and it doesn't help that they are in middle of nowhere because the enviroment is not that interesting. In the end just a bland mess. 2/5
